40" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hRnmEGVuUWZZfo1RldqTYDgqzGxYUZqQFia3QfrzibdlDicpUhVJI26Puw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">作为提供一站式便民服务的</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">翰林民众联络所</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">同样在</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">“思业，思境，思新”</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">的“三思”工作理念下</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">践行着自己的“园区速度”</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"><br  /></span></p><p><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.7031802120141343" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hkAQybqr43yF06f4AeQzr8zyK0g8kwRBiaA8FE88NCxTeebbgrhMnblg/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="849" style=""></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;text-align: center;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_editor" data-color="rgb(55, 74, 174)"><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50px;text-align: right;transform: rotate(180deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);-moz-transform: rotate(180deg);-o-transform: rotate(180deg);"><section style="width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 10px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 30px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 50px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section></section><section style="background: rgb(238, 238, 238);padding-left: 4px;display: inline-block;border-radius: 0px 20px;margin-right: 7px;margin-left: 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);padding: 5px 10px;border-radius: 0px 20px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.8em;"><p style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #ac1d10;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;">管理变革 效率为王</span></p></section></section><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;border-top: 1px solid #ffffff;margin-top: -1px;height: 1px;width: 70%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);" data-width="70%"></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50px;"><section style="width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 10px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 30px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 50px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">为杜绝日常工作中因记忆和麻痹大意而出现的或多或少的错误，提供更优质的为民服务，月亮湾社工委自2011年起在工作中创新运用了业务办理的标准化管理体系-ISO管理体系。通过制定作业指导书和说明清单的方式，规范办事流程，把工作流程从依靠回忆和经验，变成可视化的强制约束，保证重要环节不被遗漏。ISO管理体系层层传导，更成为翰林民众联络所在管理上的重大变革。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90911" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#374aae" data-custom="#374aae"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 24px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.691358024691358" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hmib36ww3J9grGibmGwIHPB0UJvNx62Ohudg8W5aj9WeBpSFatLtaou6g/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>权力下放</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">除ISO管理体系带来从以往的“自上而下”到当下“自下而上”的权力运转格局的变化。业务办理流程中各个层级的权力、责任、义务更加明确，可迅速确认民众联络所可以受理业务范围及其他部门业务范畴。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90912" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#374aae" data-custom="#374aae"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 23px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.691358024691358" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hdXvBlAic1af6gx9B1o9jFls2raaYfgWVLOtzxrzQGY2fvZEcibay2yOw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>简化流程</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">ISO管理体系并不是“无所不包”，但却简单、可测、高效。从众多的文件条文中，选择出真正适用于各个辖区特殊情况的办事依据，化繁为简，快速解决问题。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90913" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#374aae" data-custom="#374aae"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 24px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.6666666666666667" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hI9u3PpVFibE0iapib3puSl5qsSXN0keI8icib1rXk6Rj0NtfqJd5SW7mIzw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;vertical-align:middle;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>激活团队</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">ISO管理体系的制定提高了翰林民众联络所团队的凝聚力和潜能。面对较为复杂的业务，团队各成员按流程合理的分工，发挥各自最大价值，新成员的加入或其他部门的同事代班，互不熟悉也不影响协同办事，各项工作无缝接入。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"><br  /></span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"><br  /></span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"></span></p><section data-role="outer" label="Powered by 135editor.com" style="font-size:16px;"><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="91122" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#ac1d10" data-custom="#ac1d10"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:flex;display: -webkit-flex;justify-content: center;"><section style="width: 24px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img class="" data-ratio="1.6419753086419753" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hRZ3VSzniavNdT6zlBoBfFhAsXkWFcRum630wWR0VoI3libmNLdtN3icAw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section><section style="background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 30px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;padding: 0.26em 20px;text-overflow: ellipsis;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;"><strong>快速迭代</strong></span></section></section></section></section><section data-role="paragraph" class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><p><br  /></p></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">在ISO管理体系下，工作人员会系统性的将新政策、新情况转变为实用的操作方法，更新作业指导书、出具最新说明清单，实现从新政策到应用的迅速转化，可以说独一无二的“月亮湾速度”。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.7031802120141343" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hFXJic9kwnB1vMb0L1U08diaGrywLCggeiaicW3WEQp6ZH4quI4OKFhO7Vw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="849" style=""></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><br  /></p><section class="_editor" data-color="rgb(55, 74, 174)"><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50px;text-align: right;transform: rotate(180deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);-moz-transform: rotate(180deg);-o-transform: rotate(180deg);"><section style="width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 10px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 30px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 50px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section></section><section style="background: rgb(238, 238, 238);padding-left: 4px;display: inline-block;border-radius: 0px 20px;margin-right: 7px;margin-left: 7px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);padding: 5px 10px;border-radius: 0px 20px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.8em;"><p style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #ac1d10;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;">不忘初心 &nbsp;以人为本</span></p></section></section><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;border-top: 1px solid #ffffff;margin-top: -1px;height: 1px;width: 70%;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);" data-width="70%"></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50px;"><section style="width: 40px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 10px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 30px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section><section style="width: 50px;margin-top: 8px;height: 1px;background: #ac1d10;color: #ffffff;"></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">ISO管理体系的高效服务外，翰林民众联络所也注重服务的人性化，不忘初心，以人为本，积极探索和践行自己的服务模式，为居民提供特色服务，致力于成为一种超越“平台”的服务中心。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90911" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 24px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.691358024691358" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hmib36ww3J9grGibmGwIHPB0UJvNx62Ohudg8W5aj9WeBpSFatLtaou6g/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>个性化服务对口各类群体</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">翰林民众联络所分类不同居民群体的多样需求，打造各具特色的品牌服务。针对有交友意愿的单身青年，成立“创新青年汇”交友俱乐部，助力青年精英扎根园区，服务园区；针对有人文需求的居民，打造 “慧满艺课堂”，在让优秀文化荟萃交融，让月亮湾人拥有更胜一筹的智慧和才能；针对有创业需求的居民，举办创业分享沙龙，介绍园区最新的创业政策，给创业者或有意向创业者提供一个交流和分享的平台等等……有的放矢的提供个性化的服务，吸收了一批批核心的居民，形成了各种社群。</span></p><p><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.66640625" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hUG9LRl56DDjSa8fpRiauiclPL3weDYxVNAOJvziaWG512w4Fn5lNKrKFA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" style=""></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><br  /><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"></span></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90912" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 23px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.691358024691358" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hdXvBlAic1af6gx9B1o9jFls2raaYfgWVLOtzxrzQGY2fvZEcibay2yOw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>互动式运营提升服务取向</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">翰林民众联络所通过良好的互动机制和运营能力，不断提高社群的活跃度。通过微信、微博了解居民需求，通过智慧社区发布活动信息，在成熟的内容平台和连接渠道下进行多样性的表达，将有共同需求意向的居民联结在一起，开展他们关注和需要的工作和活动，保持和提升活跃度。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90913" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;text-align:center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display:inline-block;"><section style="float: left;background-color: #ac1d10;width: 24px;color: #ffffff;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.6666666666666667" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hI9u3PpVFibE0iapib3puSl5qsSXN0keI8icib1rXk6Rj0NtfqJd5SW7mIzw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="81" data-width="100%" style="display:block;width:100%;vertical-align:middle;"></section><section style="padding-left: 30px;padding-right: 20px;background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);line-height: 40px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;box-sizing: border-box;" class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><strong>专业性工作打造品牌文化</strong></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">翰林民众联络所依托“创新青年汇”和“慧满艺课堂”等品牌活动，在人群凝聚、服务提档过程中，跳出原有基层服务中心框架，成为拥有可扩展性、可连接性、自建流量平台能力的全新服务中心。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hQUW2dDE8Bs2ATQhCYPvsInhyznhVtFFsukmDpvHYXRvibcDTCQzH5LA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" style=""></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;">便民服务只有起点而无终点</span></strong></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;">翰林民众联络所对于</span></strong></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;">服务的追求，永无止境！</span></strong></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.23706896551724138" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvkzjXicjavOTwgmPW81aEp4hfjiaA4LGRsy3N7Q7Rzy1j1uibTFJcEQwJXmic7GKIOiajTcfp2joXlf5WQ/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="696"></p></section></section>
